{
  "stem": "25651.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we just visited this uncle to see whether the furniture that was in the flat fetched any money, and from what I remember, Dov Behr was rather brusque with my father.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's the first time that I saw someone talk somewhat disrespectfully to my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, it was his uncle, you see, so he was much, much senior to my father, who was then in his early 50s, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my father was an imposing man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, he-- the people weren't rude to him because he was-- you know, he was [NON-ENGLISH], he was a-- you could look at him and see that he was a man of importance.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But this was the first time that I've ever seen anyone talk to-- talk down to my father.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my uncle sort of said, there's no money left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I had to pay the cleaners because the flat was terribly dirty when Josef died, and in fact, I made a loss on it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I didn't quite understand the conversation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The conversation, obviously, took place in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I knew Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was like a third language.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I'll tell you later why.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And when we walked out of the shop, we walked down this lane, downhill, because Father had some other errand to-- to go and visit somebody, and I-- and he was holding my hand.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I asked Father, why his uncle, was so rude to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And [LAUGHS] I remember it so distinctly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Father said, oh, he thinks his ancestor was a greater rabbi than mine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, quite a lot in some ways but very little in other ways.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Novy Jicin, as I said, was a German town.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
